      <title>Bunds擦除了历史性的下降，因为飞往安全的航班减轻了债务成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bunds-erase-historic-drop-as-flight-to-safety-eases-debt-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）广泛的关税宣布之后，投资者寻求该地区最安全的债务，德国的债券集会了，消除了上个月借贷成本的历史性激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bunds-erase-historic-drop-as-flight-to-safety-eases-debt-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:17:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国将印度推出谈判中引渡了推翻的领导者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bangladesh-presses-india-to-extradite-toppled-leader-in-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国领导人穆罕默德·尤努斯（Muhammad Yunus）重申了该国的要求，即在周五与印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪（Narendra Modi）的一次会议上，印度被罢免的领导人谢赫·哈西娜（Sheikh Hasina）上周五。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bangladesh-presses-india-to-extradite-toppled-leader-in-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:14:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国以34％的美国商品关税对特朗普的关税打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/china-imposes-34-tariffs-on-all-us-imports-as-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国通过一系列措施对新的美国关税进行报复；包括对所有美国进出口的征税和稀土上的出口控制权；在唐纳德·特朗普总统施加职责并升级贸易斗争之后，兑现了罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/china-imposes-34-tariffs-on-all-us-imports-as-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票自2020年以来最糟糕的一周，随着贸易战的扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/european-stocks-extend-drop-set-for-worst-week-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国对美国关税的报复，欧洲股票下降，并进行更正，并进一步升级了全球贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/european-stocks-extend-drop-set-for-worst-week-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 07:21:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的制药评论引发了警告，印度股票低落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/pharma-stocks-in-india-sink-as-trump-says-tariffs-under-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统的评论说，美国仍在考虑对制药产品的关税之后，印第安人的股票跌倒了。]]></description>
